## B E I N 9  POSSESSED

'It starts with a sudden shudder, rising from your toes and going up your spine and into  your soul. There's a  quick,  cold pain, right in  your heart,  and then it's  like  you're  standing  a  step  behind yourself.  You're  just watching  a  movie, and your skin feels either too tight or too loose. You really start to  know what those big, awkward steam shovels and cranes on construction sites would feel if  they could feel anything.

